text:
Amana-chan, Tenka-chan... You both looked so
wonderful, like you stepped out of a storybook.
I have to do my best too!

I'm glad you're determined,
but it's okay to relax a bit more.

I thought the natural Chiyuki was suitable as one of
ALSTROEMERIA, so I decided to go with this lineup.

I feel like I might be overthinking things
a bit...

This kind of cuteness,
and that sort of... atmosphere...

So, instead of just feeling intimidated,
I want to do my best at what I can do...!
